import axios from 'axios'; import React,{useEffect, useState} from 'react' import {Link, useNavigate, useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; export default function EditUser() { let navigate=useNavigate(); const {id}=useParams() const [user,setUser] = useState({ name:"", username:"", email:"", sem1: "", sem2: "", sem3: "" }) const{name,username,email,sem1,sem2,sem3}=user const onInputChange=(e)=>{ setUser({...user,[e.target.name]:e.target.value}); }; useEffect(()=>{ loadUser() },[]); const onSubmit=async(e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); await axios.put(`http://localhost:8080/user/${id}`,user) navigate("/") } const loadUser = async()=>{ const result= await axios.get(`http://localhost:8080/user/${id}`) setUser(result.data) } return
